# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file. This change log follows the conventions of [keepachangelog.com](http://keepachangelog.com/).

## 0.9.0-SNAPSHOT - 2019-10-13
### Added
- Ensuring ordering for phrases with slop

## 0.4.0-SNAPSHOT - 2019-10-12
### Added
- Tokenizer can be specified for every dictionary entry
- Java Interface accepts tokenizer string
- Highlighter options support for text analysis options
### Changed
- Use MultiPhraseQuery instead of PhraseQuery internally

## 0.3.1 - 2019-10-03
### Fixed
- Java interface for phrase highlighting

## 0.3.0 - 2019-09-24
### Added
- Performance optimizations
### Changed
- Refactored code towards batch document highlighting

## 0.2.0 - 2019-09-24
### Added
- Alpha version for Lucene query support

## 0.1.7 - 2019-09-20
### Added
- Deployment to Maven Central

## 0.1.6 - 2019-09-19
### Added
- Added Java interface
### Fixed
- Concurrent usage

## 0.1.5 - 2019-09-16
### Fixed
- Handling of cases when text or phrases are tokenized to 0 tokens

## 0.1.4 - 2019-09-10
### Added
- Phrase slop support

## 0.1.3 - 2019-09-04
### Added
- Use one Lucene Monitor in total

## 0.1.2 - 2019-09-03
### Added
- Support for stemming for multiple languages

## 0.1.1 - 2019-08-26
### Added
- Initial release
